code: @Override protected KinesisDataFetcher<T> createFetcher(List<String> streams, SourceFunction.SourceContext<T> sourceContext, RuntimeContext runtimeContext, Properties configProps, KinesisDeserializationSchema<T> deserializationSchema) {     return new DynamoDBStreamsDataFetcher<T>(streams, sourceContext, runtimeContext, configProps, deserializationSchema, getShardAssigner()). }
